    "Furthermore, Urban Heritage and Sacred Heritage behave similarly to reCon3D and are frequent in all periods, but especially in those with a lower number of cases, such as Neolithic and Late Medieval periods.These results suggest that the heritage characteristics have an influence on the development of virtual reconstructions for iVR.",
